rockpaperscissors82 Can you tell me how the playoffs work? When will you have the final result of team blake?

The playoffs were changed this year and the rules for how the contestants will make the top 3 artists from each team to then make the top 12 are as follows:
Round 1 of the Playoffs: 
During the first round all of the Top 24 contestants perform for the votes of the public. The artist with the highest amount of votes on each team directly advanced to the Top 12, receiving immunity from the Round 2 eliminations, and left the remaining 5 artists from each team to perform again in Round 2.
Round 2 of the Playoffs:
During the second round of the playoffs the 20 remaining artists perform a second time for the votes of the public (this vote is separate from the Round 1 vote and won‚Äôt include those votes in their total). The highest vote-getter will get one spot and the coach's choice will get the remaining 3rd spot from each team. They will then join the other four artists from Round 1 and make the Top 12.
